{{infobox book | <!-- See [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Novels]] or [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Books]] --> | name = Beschreibung eines Kampfes | author = [[Franz Kafka]] | language = German | genre = [[short stories]] | publisher = Editor [[Max Brod]] | release_date = {{start date|1936}} | pages = | isbn = | oclc= }} {{infobox book | <!-- See [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Novels]] or [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Books]] --> | name = Description of a Struggle | image = DescriptionOfAStruggle.jpg | image_size = 175px | caption = First edition | author = [[Franz Kafka]] | illustrator = | cover_artist = | translator = [[James Stern|Tania and James Stern]] | country = United States | language = English | series = | genre = [[short stories]] | publisher = [[Schocken Books]] | release_date = {{start date|1958}} | isbn = | oclc= }}
'''''Description of a Struggle''''' is a collection of short stories and story fragments by [[Franz Kafka]].<ref>{{cite book |last=Gray |first= Richard |date=September 2000|title=A Franz Kafka Encyclopedia |url= |location= United States|publisher= Greenwood|pages= 31–35|isbn= 978-0313303753}}</ref> First published in 1936 after Kafka's death by [[Max Brod]], they were translated by Tania and James Stern and were published in 1958 by [[Schocken Books]].
==Contents== * [[Description of a Struggle]] * [[Blumfeld, an Elderly Bachelor]] * [[The Warden of the Tomb]] * [[The Refusal]] * Short pieces: ** [[Poseidon (short story)|Poseidon]] ** [[The Vulture (short story)|The Vulture]] ** [[The Departure (short story)|The Departure]] ** [[Give It Up! (short story)|Give It Up!]] ** [[At Night (short story)|At Night]] ** [[The Helmsman (short story)|The Helmsman]] ** [[The Top (short story)|The Top]] ** [[The Test (short story)|The Test]] ** [[Advocates]] ** [[Home-Coming (short story)|Home-Coming]] ** [[Fellowship (short story)|Fellowship]] ** Fragments of [[A Report to an Academy]] ** Fragment of [[The Great Wall of China (Kafka)|The Great Wall of China]] ** [[The Conscription of Troops]] ** Fragment of [[The Hunter Gracchus]]
==Printings== Kafka, Franz. ''Description of a Struggle''. New York: Schocken Books, 1958.
