{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2018}} {{Use Indian English|date=April 2018}} '''Zee Gaurav Puraskar''' is a cinema award show in India initiated by [[Zee Network]] to reward excellence in the [[Marathi language|Marathi]] entertainment world.
[[Neha Rajpal]] has won the prestigious Zee Gaurav Puraskar for best Female Playback Singing in year 2008 for her song "Fulnara Mausam" from film "Mukkam post London"<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.zeemarathi.com/ZeeGaurav_Nominations_PDF/ZGauravWinners.pdf|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107070755/http://zeemarathi.com/ZeeGaurav_Nominations_PDF/ZGauravWinners.pdf|archivedate=2012-11-07 |format=pdf |series=Nominees of Zee Gaurav Puraskar |title=Zee Gaurav Winners |deadurl=no |accessdate=2013-01-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.indiantelevision.com/headlines/y2k9/feb/feb44.php |title='Jogwa' bags 12 nominations in Zee Marathi's 'Gaurav Puraskaar' |publisher=Indian Television Dot Com |date=2009-02-05 |accessdate=2010-07-23}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.televisionpoint.com/news2009/newsfullstory.php?id=1233921449 |title=Zee Gaurav Puraskar 2009 on February 21 |publisher=Televisionpoint.com |date=2009-02-06 |accessdate=2010-07-23}}</ref>
